                            <comment id="330548" author="jhammond" created="Tue, 29 Mar 2022 20:08:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed by &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8950&quot; title=&quot;tests: sanity-hsm: use make_custom_file_for_progress() as little as possible&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-8950&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-8950&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (tests: do not use make_custom_file_for_progress()).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="176522" author="pjones" created="Mon, 5 Dec 2016 18:37:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;John is investigating&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="176470" author="jhammond" created="Mon, 5 Dec 2016 14:56:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Here and in several other test scripts we should be using &apos;kill -0 $pid&apos; instead of various contraptions based on &apos;ps&apos;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
